name: Imam Kikou - Song is Alone (Remastered)
description: An audio visual remastered from the original song "Song is Alone" by Imam Kikou that created it's visual by Mamedz a.k.a. Totemnica Sandiwara. The song itself told about the desperation being lonely in a hard times, including lose your jobs, your lover, passion, etc. And this song represent what it feels like when Imam Kikou on his downfall.
